        md: 'Stage 1 intent check:\nHi [Parent], we missed you at [Athlete]’s meeting with Coach [Scout].\nIf you still want a recruiting game plan, reply:\n1. Still interested, reschedule.\n2. Interested, bad timing.\n3. No longer interested.\n\nStage 2 direct check:\nHi [Parent], I saw interest, but we still need a time.\nReply 1 or 2 for the slots, or 3 to close this out for now.\n\nFinal check:\nHi [Parent], last check before I close this out.\nIf [Athlete] still wants a recruiting game plan, pick a slot today.',
